wall.
Turning
from
the
pale
phantom
which
reflected
herself
in
its
outline,
and
her
reverie
in
the
drooped
attitude
of
its
dim
head
and
colourless
tresses,
she
sat
down
inaction
would
suit
the
frame
of
mind
into
which
